data.description: If you love to be in Atlanta, then this is your chance to Uncover True Southern Charm in the Heart of Atlanta's West End with easy access to I-20, I-75, and I-85 making it an Ideal choice for professionals and families alike.    This meticulously renovated masterpiece blends modern elegance and charm creating an unmatched living experience.    Nestled on a beautifully landscaped 0.3-acre lot, this property exudes curb appeal from the moment you arrive with the inviting front porch, deck, and breathtaking manicured fenced backyard creating the perfect setting for alfresco dining, and entertaining. The open-concept living area features soaring ceilings, gleaming hardwood floors, and an abundance of natural light pouring in through the oversized windows. The primary suite, with a spa-inspired bathroom, features a freestanding soaking tub, and a massive walk-in closet. The gourmet kitchen, boasts top-tier appliances, and custom cabinetry.    A completely refined and built with all custom upgrades ticking all the needs to make it the best family space to experience.
